  meanings
    entry
      definitions
        entry
          definition "An expression used to show contentment for something"
          example "Mmm, this is a tasty pie!"
        entry
          definition "An expression used to show thought or reflection"
          example "Mmm, I see what you mean."
        entry
          definition 'An expression used to show being muffled or not able to speak clearly, as well as "mmph".'
        entry
          definition Yes.
      partOfSpeech interjection
    entry
      definitions
        entry
          definition "A period into which a year is divided, historically based on the phases of the moon."
          example "July is my favourite month."
        entry
          definition "A period of 30 days, 31 days, or some alternation thereof."
          example "We went on holiday for two months."
        entry
          definition "(in the plural) A woman's period; menstrual discharge."
      partOfSpeech noun
